section.animate-in.space-y-4
	a.nav-link.text-sm.inline-flex.items-center.gap-1(href="/examples") ← examples
	h1.text-5xl.font-bold.tracking-tight.leading-none
		span.gradient-text Norns
	p.text-lg.text-neutral-600.max-w-prose.leading-relaxed
		| Apps using Norns conventions — Pug + CoffeeScript in
		code .n
		| files.

section.animate-in-delayed.pt-12
	.grid.gap-3(class="sm:grid-cols-2")
		a.card-interactive(href="/examples/norns/todo")
			.flex.items-start.justify-between.gap-3.mb-2
				h2.font-semibold.text-lg Todo
				span.text-xs.text-neutral-400.font-mono.shrink-0.mt-1 .n
			p.text-sm.text-neutral-600.leading-relaxed components, props, Svelte stores, lists, scoped CSS
		a.card-interactive(href="/examples/norns/tic-tac-toe")
			.flex.items-start.justify-between.gap-3.mb-2
				h2.font-semibold.text-lg Tic Tac Toe
				span.text-xs.text-neutral-400.font-mono.shrink-0.mt-1 .n
			p.text-sm.text-neutral-600.leading-relaxed 1v1 or vs computer, with derived state and AI heuristic
		a.card-interactive(href="/examples/norns/menu")
			.flex.items-start.justify-between.gap-3.mb-2
				h2.font-semibold.text-lg Menu
				span.text-xs.text-neutral-400.font-mono.shrink-0.mt-1 .n
			p.text-sm.text-neutral-600.leading-relaxed JSON endpoint with GET / POST, table view, debounced search
		a.card-interactive(href="/examples/norns/notes")
			.flex.items-start.justify-between.gap-3.mb-2
				h2.font-semibold.text-lg Notes
				span.text-xs.text-neutral-400.font-mono.shrink-0.mt-1 .n
			p.text-sm.text-neutral-600.leading-relaxed SQLite + form actions, dynamic routes, +error.n, SSR load
